21
00:02:14,130 --> 00:02:15,220
What is troubling you?

22
00:02:15,270 --> 00:02:16,300
Marry someone as you wish.

23
00:02:16,820 --> 00:02:17,740
Why are you waiting for me?

24
00:02:20,660 --> 00:02:21,660
How come the words

25
00:02:21,660 --> 00:02:23,060
