26
00:02:30,660 --> 00:02:31,579
Ex-girlfriend?

27
00:02:38,310 --> 00:02:39,310
That's it.

28
00:02:40,630 --> 00:02:42,090
She's good-looking

29
00:02:42,150 --> 00:02:43,310
