30
00:02:44,380 --> 00:02:44,860
So back then,

31
00:02:44,890 --> 00:02:46,000
why did you break up?

32
00:02:48,460 --> 00:02:49,220
Let's do the room check.

33
00:02:51,340 --> 00:02:52,220
Wait.

34
