It's sour

39
00:03:27,460 --> 00:03:28,540
and sweet.

40
00:03:29,500 --> 00:03:30,260
The taste

41
00:03:30,780 --> 00:03:31,900
is amazing.

42
00:03:41,440 --> 00:03:42,240
Try one.

43
00:03:43,579 --> 00:03:44,420
If it doesn't taste good,

44
00:03:44,420 --> 00:03:45,500
I'll pay with my life.

45
00:04:06,940 --> 00:04:07,900
Amazing.

46
00:04:08,470 --> 00:04:09,390
Truly amazing.

