00:30:30,400 --> 00:30:31,550
of being indifferent to everyone,

592
00:30:31,580 --> 00:30:32,620
who would like her?

593
00:30:32,910 --> 00:30:33,950
Only my brother

594
00:30:33,980 --> 00:30:35,300
treated her as a treasure.

595
00:30:35,500 --> 00:30:36,060
In the past few years,

596
00:30:36,090 --> 00:30:37,480
she found out no one else liked her.

597
00:30:37,790 --> 00:30:39,110
So it reminds her of my brother.

598
00:30:39,600 --> 00:30:40,590
Why do I feel

599
00:30:40,620 --> 00:30:42,260
something is wrong with your brother recently?

600
00:30:44,750 --> 00:30:46,260
Does he still like her?

601
00:30:46,990 --> 00:30:48,150
No way.

602
00:30:48,180 --> 00:30:49,380
My brother must have hated her so much.

603
00:30:49,400 --> 00:30:50,840
How could he like her?

604
00:30:51,500 --> 00:30:52,780
You don't understand.

605
00:30:52,840 --> 00:30:53,860
I've arranged so many blind dates

606
00:30:53,860 --> 00:30:55,260
for your brother these years.

607
00:30:55,370 --> 00:30:56,780
Either he said he was too busy

608
00:30:56,780 --> 00:30:57,460
to go on dates,

609
00:30:57,460 --> 00:30:58,460
or he went on the dates

610
00:30:58,460 --> 00:30:59,460
and said he didn't fall for the girls.

611
00:31:00,340 --> 00:31:01,660
No way.

612
00:31:01,880 --> 00:31:03,140
Even if my brother is single all his life,

613
00:31:03,140 --> 00:31:04,380
he can't be with her.

614
00:31:04,380 --> 00:31:04,900
Has he forgotten

615
00:31:04,900 --> 00:31:06,140
how badly he was hurt?

616
00:31:06,140 --> 00:31:06,740
Well...

617
00:31:07,630 --> 00:31:08,180
No way.

618
00:31:08,220 --> 00:31:09,620
I have to make a phone call to wake him up.

619
00:31:10,800 --> 00:31:12,190
I can't believe he tends to be abused.

620
00:31:12,230 --> 00:31:13,020
Isn't this...

621
00:31:14,140 --> 00:31:15,020
My dear,

622
00:31:15,050 --> 00:31:15,920
don't mind

623
00:31:15,940 --> 00:31:17,020
your brother's business.

624
00:31:24,010 --> 00:31:25,890
Stop tapping your foot. Go and study.

