00:32:00,730 --> 00:32:01,660
My baby is burnt.

628
00:32:01,660 --> 00:32:02,740
Please check on her.

629
00:32:02,820 --> 00:32:03,750
Have you registered?

630
00:32:04,440 --> 00:32:05,570
Do we need to register for the emergency?

631
00:32:05,570 --> 00:32:06,900
Emergency needs to be registered too.

632
00:32:06,900 --> 00:32:07,500
What kind of hospital is this?

633
00:32:07,500 --> 00:32:09,180
I'm already burnt like this.

634
00:32:09,200 --> 00:32:10,190
The man should go to register first.

635
00:32:10,380 --> 00:32:11,750
Otherwise, we can't prescribe medicine in the system.

636
00:32:11,910 --> 00:32:12,620
Fine.

637
00:32:12,650 --> 00:32:13,650
Wait for me.

638
00:32:14,600 --> 00:32:15,530
You may leave too.

639
00:32:15,550 --> 00:32:16,300
Thank you.

640
00:32:16,340 --> 00:32:17,530
Please go out first.

641
00:32:22,730 --> 00:32:23,650
Go get the medicine

642
00:32:23,700 --> 00:32:24,890
and take her to get an injection.

643
00:32:24,910 --> 00:32:25,630
Okay.

644
00:32:25,660 --> 00:32:26,700
If you get bitten by a dog again,

645
00:32:26,720 --> 00:32:28,570
you can directly go to the Center for Disease Control and Prevention.

646
00:32:28,600 --> 00:32:29,710
You don't have to come to the general hospital.

647
00:32:29,910 --> 00:32:31,320
Okay, thank you.

648
00:32:36,820 --> 00:32:38,220
Doctor, hurry up.

649
00:32:38,370 --> 00:32:39,780
Let me see.

650
00:32:40,010 --> 00:32:41,010
There's skin redness here.

651
00:32:41,030 --> 00:32:41,960
I burnt myself.

652
00:32:41,990 --> 00:32:42,780
How?

653
00:32:42,820 --> 00:32:43,660
I accidentally burnt myself

654
00:32:43,680 --> 00:32:44,720
when I was boiling the water.

655
00:32:44,900 --> 00:32:45,650
Did it happen just now?

656
00:32:47,700 --> 00:32:48,700
It's done registering. Here.

657
00:32:50,050 --> 00:32:50,650
It's okay.

658
00:32:50,670 --> 00:32:51,580
Blow it.

659
00:32:55,430 --> 00:32:57,150
Will it leave a scar?

660
00:32:57,620 --> 00:32:59,040
It's okay. Relax.

661
00:33:01,780 --> 00:33:03,260
Here, this is the prescription.

662
00:33:03,340 --> 00:33:04,480
Just take the medicine according to this.

663
00:33:04,550 --> 00:33:05,870
That's all? Is it done?

664
00:33:06,020 --> 00:33:06,990
You're not badly injured.

665
00:33:07,020 --> 00:33:07,860
Just apply it for three days.

666
00:33:07,880 --> 00:33:09,470
It's so red here.

667
00:33:09,880 --> 00:33:10,520
Dr Xu.

668
00:33:10,550 --> 00:33:10,820
What's wrong?

669
00:33:10,860 --> 00:33:11,340
A firefighter

670
00:33:11,340 --> 00:33:12,210
is seriously injured.

671
00:33:12,210 --> 00:33:12,940
Take a look.

672
00:33:12,940 --> 00:33:13,540
Take a look.

673
00:33:15,270 --> 00:33:15,820
Doctor.

674
00:33:18,840 --> 00:33:20,530
Go to the debridement room and get ready for suturing.

675
00:33:21,540 --> 00:33:22,090
Doctor.

676
00:33:22,120 --> 00:33:23,310
You haven't checked on my wife.

677
00:33:23,580 --> 00:33:24,140
Didn't I give you the prescription

678
00:33:24,140 --> 00:33:25,100
just now?

679
00:33:25,100 --> 00:33:25,450
Just get the medicine

680
00:33:25,450 --> 00:33:26,580
according to that.

681
00:33:26,600 --> 00:33:28,240
You're just done with the simple process?

682
00:33:28,420 --> 00:33:29,410
You're not seriously injured.

683
00:33:29,440 --> 00:33:30,650
Just apply the medicine according to the prescription.

684
00:33:32,740 --> 00:33:33,750
Have you treated my wife?

685
00:33:34,240 --> 00:33:35,440
You didn't even spend ten seconds.

686
00:33:35,460 --> 00:33:36,270
I don't have time

687
00:33:36,300 --> 00:33:37,210
to talk to you now. Let's go.

688
00:33:37,240 --> 00:33:38,000
[Emergency Surgery]

689
00:33:38,190 --> 00:33:39,210
[Emergency Surgery]

690
00:33:38,700 --> 00:33:39,380
Don't go.

691
00:33:39,380 --> 00:33:40,620
You're not going to treat my wife, are you?

692
00:33:43,760 --> 00:33:44,900
Why are you bullying a woman?

693
00:33:45,180 --> 00:33:46,140
Where did you learn

694
00:33:46,140 --> 00:33:47,090
the bad habit from?

695
00:33:47,180 --> 00:33:48,690
Who are you? I'm looking for her...

696
00:33:49,590 --> 00:33:50,670
Can't you stop?

697
00:33:50,710 --> 00:33:52,430
Let go of my husband.

698
00:33:51,710 --> 00:33:54,040
[Emergency Surgery]

699
00:33:54,980 --> 00:33:55,790
Are you not going to save people,

700
00:33:55,820 --> 00:33:56,820
but being an onlooker here?

701
00:33:58,350 --> 00:33:59,360
Go get the medicine.

702
00:33:59,460 --> 00:34:00,260
Let's go.

703
00:34:01,100 --> 00:34:02,100
I'll wait for you.

704
00:34:08,199 --> 00:34:08,960
Hang in there.

705
00:34:08,989 --> 00:34:10,310
I'll give you an anaesthetic soon.

706
00:34:10,830 --> 00:34:11,830
Thank you, doctor.

707
00:34:11,860 --> 00:34:13,300
Let me clean it up for you.

708
00:34:13,929 --> 00:34:14,460
Here.

709
00:34:14,480 --> 00:34:15,520
Raise your arm.

710
00:34:20,469 --> 00:34:21,989
Stop hiding.

711
00:34:22,280 --> 00:34:23,159
My right hand is fine.

712
00:34:23,190 --> 00:34:24,020
I can do it myself.

713
00:34:24,040 --> 00:34:25,489
Your right hand is still swollen.

714
00:34:25,540 --> 00:34:26,139
And dirty.

715
00:34:26,300 --> 00:34:27,580
How can you do it yourself?

716
00:34:30,900 --> 00:34:32,590
What happened to your hand?

717
00:34:33,920 --> 00:34:34,920
Someone jumped off the bridge.

718
00:34:34,940 --> 00:34:36,260
Luckily, he's fine.

719
00:34:36,320 --> 00:34:36,960
We saved him.

720
00:34:37,300 --> 00:34:38,699
Is there no ambulance at the scene?

721
00:34:39,050 --> 00:34:40,000
No.

722
00:34:40,030 --> 00:34:41,000
My colleague

723
00:34:41,030 --> 00:34:41,679
got me here

724
00:34:41,710 --> 00:34:42,480
in a hurry.

725
00:34:42,570 --> 00:34:44,690
If there's no ambulance, we should file a complaint.

726
00:34:44,840 --> 00:34:45,880
No, Dr Xu.

727
00:34:45,900 --> 00:34:46,670
The ambulance is under

728
00:34:46,699 --> 00:34:48,050
the same system as us.

729
00:34:48,350 --> 00:34:49,190
Exactly.

730
00:34:49,659 --> 00:34:51,020
A crow picked out another crow's eyes.

731
00:34:51,020 --> 00:34:52,460
We're family.

732
00:34:52,500 --> 00:34:53,920
There's nothing to complain about.

733
00:34:54,199 --> 00:34:55,080
You doctors,

734
00:34:55,170 --> 00:34:56,300
and we firefighters,

735
00:34:56,360 --> 00:34:57,710
are all friends.

736
00:34:57,750 --> 00:34:58,430
Right?

737
00:34:58,450 --> 00:34:59,650
None of us lives an easy life.

738
00:35:00,230 --> 00:35:01,320
Ready for anaesthesia.

739
00:35:02,630 --> 00:35:03,350
Please be gentle.

740
00:35:03,380 --> 00:35:05,180
I've been afraid of injections since I was young.

741
00:35:19,300 --> 00:35:20,500
Were you dead just now?

742
00:35:22,650 --> 00:35:23,940
That man was unreasonable.

743
00:35:23,980 --> 00:35:25,350
Couldn't you see he wanted to hit the doctor?

744
00:35:26,470 --> 00:35:27,200
No.

745
00:35:27,250 --> 00:35:27,980
I was just...

746
00:35:27,980 --> 00:35:28,860
If I didn't come,

747
00:35:28,880 --> 00:35:30,160
would you watch her get beaten up?

748
00:35:30,270 --> 00:35:31,600
Impossible, boss.

749
00:35:31,700 --> 00:35:32,900
Besides, he didn't hit her.

750
00:35:32,930 --> 00:35:34,040
I'm not your boss.

751
00:35:34,200 --> 00:35:35,150
You are my boss.

752
00:35:35,890 --> 00:35:36,730
You...

753
00:35:39,500 --> 00:35:40,740
Wait.

754
00:35:43,220 --> 00:35:44,630
Do you know that doctor?

755
00:35:47,930 --> 00:35:48,770
No, I don't.

756
00:35:49,270 --> 00:35:49,980
You don't know her?

757
00:35:49,980 --> 00:35:51,380
Why are you so worried about her?

758
00:36:10,750 --> 00:36:11,540
Jiang, how are you?

759
00:36:11,560 --> 00:36:12,280
I'm fine.

760
00:36:12,790 --> 00:36:13,820
Thank you, doctor.

761
00:36:13,920 --> 00:36:14,560
Pay the bill first.

762
00:36:14,580 --> 00:36:15,660
Then, prescribe him anti-inflammatory medicine.

763
00:36:14,640 --> 00:36:17,860
[Fire Hydrant]

764
00:36:15,690 --> 00:36:16,300
Okay.

765
00:36:16,340 --> 00:36:17,170
Thank you, nurse.

766
00:36:17,170 --> 00:36:17,910
Thank you, doctor.

767
00:36:19,110 --> 00:36:19,890
Looking for someone?

768
00:36:19,840 --> 00:36:24,430
[Fire Hydrant]

769
00:36:20,250 --> 00:36:21,080
Our chief just left.

770
00:36:21,100 --> 00:36:21,870
He went that way.

771
00:36:24,460 --> 00:36:25,540
Go get the medicine.

772
00:36:26,210 --> 00:36:26,970
Thank you.

773
00:36:27,140 --> 00:36:27,690
We'll go now.

774
00:36:27,730 --> 00:36:28,570
Thank you, nurse.

775
00:36:29,260 --> 00:36:30,030
Are you okay?

